 name to India Glycols Limited in August 1986. India Glycols Limited was incorporated in 1983 and is headquartered in Noida, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 1357, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Uma Shankar Bhartia", "age": 72, "title": "Chairman & MD", "yearBorn": 1953, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 152498841, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Rupark  Sarswat", "age": 53, "title": "Chief Executive Officer", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Anand  Singhal FCA", "age": 59, "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1966, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Atul  Govil", "title": "CTO and Head of SAP & IT", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Ankur  Jain", "age": 50, "title": "Head of Legal, Compliance Officer & Company Secretary", "yearBorn": 1975, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Pragya Bhartia Barwale", "age": 43, "title": "Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1982, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 60229596, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Alok  Singhal", "age": 55, "title": "Whole-time Director", "yearBorn": 1970, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 8969211, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Sudhir  Agarwal", "age": 63, "title": "President Operations", "yearBorn": 1962, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 7509089, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Madhup  Misra", "age": 62, "title": "Head  of Account & Admin", "yearBorn": 1963, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Dev Chander Jha", "age": 46, "title": "Chief Human Resource Officer", "yearBorn": 1979, "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue"